name: Classic Rum Tiramisu
description: Bittersweet and mysterious, this is the classic tiramisu recipe at its very best. Uses either Myer's dark rum or Bacardi superior black rum.

name: Vanilla Dream Tiramisu
description: Chocolate shavings in Hokkaido milk and vanilla beans make this a favorite of kids from 1 to 92. Uses decaf coffee

name: Baileys Tiramisu
description: This new cocktail-inspired limited edition liqueur combines the deliciousness of Baileys Irish Cream with the decadent flavours of a tiramisu dessert

name: Earl Grey Grand Marnier Tiramisu
description: Earl grey bergamot is layered onto an orange cognac base - fruit tea-ramisu, anyone?

name: Blackforest Tiramisu
description: Luscious cherries x Kirsch liquor, modeled after our founder's favorite cake!

name: Patrón XO Cafe Coffee Liqueuer Tiramisu
description: Robust flavors of fresh-roasted coffee, fine chocolate and light tequila. Perfect for coffee lovers!

name: Otard Cognac Tiramisu
description: An elegant and full-bodied tiramisu with vanilla, earthy tobacco and fruity note, like the VSOP cognac it uses! Finishes with a nice length.

name: Black Nikka Special Whisky Tiramisu
description: Earthy and Chocolatey with a hint of fruity sweetness, this whisky is a winning combination of dark chocolate, warm spices and berry fruit making it the perfect liquor for tiramisu

name: Friends Size Tiramisu - Perfect for 5!
description: Perfectly sized at 880ml in volume, this tiramisu is good to share among 5 to 6 people in this new world! Choose from any flavor of the week. Comes in our signature eco-friendly airtight glass dish with bamboo lid.
